OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with occasional rain or
OL,6,Fdrizzle, this turning more persistent
OL,7,Ffor a time in the afternoon for
OL,8,FShetland. Drier across Orkney later.
OL,9,FFresh to strong southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mainly dry start to the
OL,12,Fevening once rain clears Shetland.
OL,13,FLater in the night outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fwill spread into Orkney then Shetland.
OL,15,FFresh southerly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,18,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,19,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,20,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,21,Fbecoming fewer. Fresh to strong winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
